trans-unit.source: Represents an immutable (read-only) pair of "Name" and "Description" strings.
trans-unit.target: "이름" 및 "설명" 문자열의 변경이 불가능한(읽기 전용) 쌍을 나타냅니다.

trans-unit.source: <xref:System.Security.RightsManagement.LocalizedNameDescriptionPair> is a basic building block for structures that express locale specific information for an <xref:System.Security.RightsManagement.UnsignedPublishLicense>.
trans-unit.target: <xref:System.Security.RightsManagement.LocalizedNameDescriptionPair> 구조에 대 한 기본 빌딩 블록에 대 한 해당 빠른 로캘 특정 정보는 <xref:System.Security.RightsManagement.UnsignedPublishLicense>합니다.

trans-unit.source: The value for the locale <see cref="P:System.Security.RightsManagement.LocalizedNameDescriptionPair.Name" /> property.
The value for the locale <see cref="P:System.Security.RightsManagement.LocalizedNameDescriptionPair.Description" /> property.
Initializes a new instance of the <see cref="T:System.Security.RightsManagement.LocalizedNameDescriptionPair" /> class.
Either the <paramref name="name" /> parameter or <paramref name="description" /> parameter is <see langword="null" />.
trans-unit.target: <paramref name="name" /> 매개 변수 또는 <paramref name="description" /> 매개 변수가 <see langword="null" />인 경우

trans-unit.source: The <xref:System.Security.RightsManagement.LocalizedNameDescriptionPair.Description%2A> property is set as a parameter to the <xref:System.Security.RightsManagement.LocalizedNameDescriptionPair.%23ctor%2A> constructor.
trans-unit.target: <xref:System.Security.RightsManagement.LocalizedNameDescriptionPair.Description%2A> 속성에 대 한 매개 변수로 <xref:System.Security.RightsManagement.LocalizedNameDescriptionPair.%23ctor%2A> 생성자입니다.

trans-unit.source: The object to compare the <see cref="P:System.Security.RightsManagement.LocalizedNameDescriptionPair.Name" /> and <see cref="P:System.Security.RightsManagement.LocalizedNameDescriptionPair.Description" /> properties of.

Indicates whether the <see cref="P:System.Security.RightsManagement.LocalizedNameDescriptionPair.Name" /> and <see cref="P:System.Security.RightsManagement.LocalizedNameDescriptionPair.Description" /> properties of a given object match those of this <see cref="T:System.Security.RightsManagement.LocalizedNameDescriptionPair" />.
trans-unit.target: 특정 개체의 <see cref="P:System.Security.RightsManagement.LocalizedNameDescriptionPair.Name" /> 및 <see cref="P:System.Security.RightsManagement.LocalizedNameDescriptionPair.Description" /> 속성이 이 <see cref="T:System.Security.RightsManagement.LocalizedNameDescriptionPair" />와 일치하는지 여부를 나타냅니다.

trans-unit.source: <see langword="true" /> if the <see cref="P:System.Security.RightsManagement.LocalizedNameDescriptionPair.Name" /> and <see cref="P:System.Security.RightsManagement.LocalizedNameDescriptionPair.Description" /> properties of the given object match those of this instance; otherwise, <see langword="false" />.
trans-unit.target: 특정 개체의 <see cref="P:System.Security.RightsManagement.LocalizedNameDescriptionPair.Name" /> 및 <see cref="P:System.Security.RightsManagement.LocalizedNameDescriptionPair.Description" /> 속성이 이 인스턴스와 일치하면 <see langword="true" />이고, 그렇지 않으면 <see langword="false" />입니다.

trans-unit.source: Gets a computed hash code based on the <see cref="P:System.Security.RightsManagement.LocalizedNameDescriptionPair.Name" /> and <see cref="P:System.Security.RightsManagement.LocalizedNameDescriptionPair.Description" /> properties.
trans-unit.target: <see cref="P:System.Security.RightsManagement.LocalizedNameDescriptionPair.Name" /> 및 <see cref="P:System.Security.RightsManagement.LocalizedNameDescriptionPair.Description" /> 속성을 기반으로 하여 계산된 해시 코드를 가져옵니다.

trans-unit.source: A computed hash code based on the <see cref="P:System.Security.RightsManagement.LocalizedNameDescriptionPair.Name" /> and <see cref="P:System.Security.RightsManagement.LocalizedNameDescriptionPair.Description" /> properties of this <see cref="T:System.Security.RightsManagement.LocalizedNameDescriptionPair" />.
trans-unit.target: 이 <see cref="T:System.Security.RightsManagement.LocalizedNameDescriptionPair" />의 <see cref="P:System.Security.RightsManagement.LocalizedNameDescriptionPair.Name" /> 및 <see cref="P:System.Security.RightsManagement.LocalizedNameDescriptionPair.Description" /> 속성을 기반으로 하여 계산된 해시 코드입니다.

trans-unit.source: The <xref:System.Security.RightsManagement.LocalizedNameDescriptionPair.Name%2A> property is set as a parameter to the <xref:System.Security.RightsManagement.LocalizedNameDescriptionPair.%23ctor%2A> constructor.
trans-unit.target: <xref:System.Security.RightsManagement.LocalizedNameDescriptionPair.Name%2A> 속성에 대 한 매개 변수로 <xref:System.Security.RightsManagement.LocalizedNameDescriptionPair.%23ctor%2A> 생성자입니다.
